@startuml

title Agentic RAG Architecture

skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor #E3F2FD
    BorderColor #1565C0
}

actor "User" as User

component "Query Encoder" as QueryEncoder
component "Document Encoder" as DocumentEncoder
component "Retriever" as Retriever
component "Generator" as Generator

database "Knowledge Base" as KnowledgeBase

User --> QueryEncoder : User query
QueryEncoder --> Retriever : Query embedding
DocumentEncoder --> KnowledgeBase : Document embeddings
KnowledgeBase --> Retriever : Relevant embeddings
Retriever --> Generator : Retrieved documents
Generator --> User : Generated response

note right of QueryEncoder
  Encodes user query
  into dense vector
end note

note right of KnowledgeBase
  Stores document embeddings
  and metadata
end note

note right of Generator
  Generates response using
  query + retrieved docs
end note

@enduml
